"noise-free imaging in scanning microscopes. Ultramicroscopy, 76 (1999) 47 "
"<ulink url=\"http://dx.doi.org/10.1016/S0304-3991(98)00074-6\">doi:10.1016/"
"S0304-3991(98)00074-6</ulink>"
msgstr ""
